The paper discusses game usability models, which are related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper mentions the integration of current approaches in game industry and game research, which could fall under the categories of cybersecurity (cs.CYBER), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
